#实验3 UI组件
#*主activity三个按钮,点击进入对应的组件*

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Noob-I-Am/UIComponent/master/pics/main.PNG)

##点击SIMPLEADAPTER显示

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Noob-I-Am/UIComponent/master/pics/adapter.png)

如图所示 点击任意一项 出现短暂toast提示所选项内容

##点击ALERTDIALOG显示

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Noob-I-Am/UIComponent/master/pics/dialog.PNG) 

##点击XMLMENU显示菜单项页面

![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Noob-I-Am/UIComponent/master/pics/menu.PNG)

如图所示，选择菜单项调整文本字体颜色大小

##ACTIONMODE展示

长按转换actionmode模式

![](https://github.com/Noob-I-Am/UIComponent/blob/master/pics/actionmode.png)
